title: Shonen Knife - Osaka Ramones
description: Shonen Knife, Japan's most notable indie musical import, celebrates their 30 anniversary w/ a tribute to The Ramones. ""Osaka Ramones"" is not only the name of this Ramones tribute album, but is also the name of the side project which has made its way in and out of Shonen Knife's performing history for decades. Osaka Ramones was recorded and mixed between Osaka, JP and New York.
